# PriceFlow Pro

Quantity-based pricing and volume discounts for Wix Stores.

## Run locally

```bash
yarn install
yarn typecheck
yarn build
yarn preview
```

## Manual setup

Replace `<app-namespace>` in `src/consts.ts` with the namespace from your Wix Dev Center app before publishing. Configure Wix App Billing plans in Dev Center for Free, Starter, Pro, Business, and Enterprise.
